"#feedbackModal_main_2532575\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 04, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104txt1665702779095.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/txt1665702779095.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/txt1665702779095.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"txt1665702779095\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Testing DSPs on Mobile Devices\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body taskbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">During development you can test the user interface on mobile devices by scanning a QR code for the URL of the dynamic server page.\n </p>\n<section><ol class=\"ol steps\"><li class=\"li step stepexpand\" id=\"txt1665702779095__li_d14372e1_d14373e1_d14374e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\">Ensure that your development web server is accessible to the mobile device, for example via a WiFi network.\n </span>\n</li><li class=\"li step stepexpand\" id=\"txt1665702779095__li_d14375e1_d14376e1_d14377e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\">Edit the logical <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">TEST_COMMAND_CPT_WEB</span> to replace <code class=\"ph codeph\">localhost</code> with the actual host name. You can specify a network address (<code class=\"ph codeph\">AMS12345D1.myorg.local</code>) or an IP number (<code class=\"ph codeph\">123.456.789.00</code>) instead. For example:\n </span>\n<div class=\"itemgroup info\">\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">;ide.asn\n[LOGICALS]\nTEST_COMMAND_CPT_WEB = http://AMS093606D2:%TomcatPort/uniface/wrd/%CptName</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</li><li class=\"li step stepexpand\" id=\"txt1665702779095__li_d14378e1_d14379e1_d14380e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\">Generate a QR code for the main DSP of your mobile app. Open the DSP and choose <span class=\"ph menucascade\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Actions &gt;Show QR Code</span></span>. </span>\n<div class=\"itemgroup info\">\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"txt1665702779095__fig_d28151e1_d28152e1_d28153e1\">\n</figure>\n</div>\n</li><li class=\"li step stepexpand\" id=\"txt1665702779095__li_d14381e1_d14382e1_d14383e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\" id=\"txt1665702779095__p_d28154e1_d28155e1_d28156e1\">Scan the QR code with your phone or tablet to run\n               the server page in your device's web browser. </span>\n<div class=\"itemgroup info\">\n<p class=\"p\">Alternatively, you can click the QR code to open it in a browser on your desktop\n                  machine, or press <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Ctrl+D</span>. </p>\n</div>\n</li><li class=\"li step stepexpand\" id=\"txt1665702779095__li_d14384e1_d14385e1_d14386e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\" id=\"txt1665702779095__p_d28157e1_d28158e1_d28159e1\">If you experience problems in displaying the\n               page, ensure that the Uniface Router and the Tomcat web service are running. </span>\n<div class=\"itemgroup info\">\n<p class=\"p\">In the Windows Services, look for the services listed under Uniface, such as\n                     <code class=\"ph codeph\">Uniface XXX Development Tomcat</code>and <code class=\"ph codeph\">Uniface XXX\n                     Development URouter</code>You can restart the services here.</p>\n</div>\n</li></ol></section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2532575\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2532575\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Testing DSPs on Mobile Devices Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 04, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Testing DSPs on Mobile Devices During development you can test the user interface on mobile devices by scanning a QR code for the URL of the dynamic server page. Ensure that your development web server is accessible to the mobile device, for example via a WiFi network. Edit the logical TEST_COMMAND_CPT_WEB to replace localhost with the actual host name. You can specify a network address ( AMS12345D1.myorg.local ) or an IP number ( 123.456.789.00 ) instead. For example: ;ide.asn [LOGICALS] TEST_COMMAND_CPT_WEB = http://AMS093606D2:%TomcatPort/uniface/wrd/%CptName Copy Generate a QR code for the main DSP of your mobile app. Open the DSP and choose Actions >Show QR Code . Scan the QR code with your phone or tablet to run the server page in your device's web browser. Alternatively, you can click the QR code to open it in a browser on your desktop machine, or press Ctrl+D . If you experience problems in displaying the page, ensure that the Uniface Router and the Tomcat web service are running. In the Windows Services, look for the services listed under Uniface, such as Uniface XXX Development Tomcat and Uniface XXX Development URouter You can restart the services here. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}